Against your contract of six hearts,|
PG| ***** 35 ***** |


AT| this time West opens a diamond,|pc|dQ|
PG| ***** 36 ***** |


AT| which you win with Dummy's Ace.|
pg| ***** 37 ***** |


pc|dA|pc|dJ|pc|d5|
PG| ***** 38 ***** |


