pg| ***** 43 ***** |


AT| You can afford to do this, for you need only three trumps in the Dummy for ruffing spades.|
PG| ***** 44 ***** |


NT|^B@2
Proceeding with your cross-ruff, you trump spades in the Dummy|
pg| ***** 45 ***** |


pc|s7|pc|s5|pc|sA|pc|sT|
PG| ***** 46 ***** |


pc|s4|pc|sK|pc|h3|pc|s2|
pg| ***** 47 ***** |


AT| and lead diamonds|pc|d2|
PG| ***** 48 ***** |


AT| to ruff in your own hand.|pc|dK|pc|h7|pc|d7|
PG| ***** 49 ***** |


AT| It now makes very little difference to you what cards the Opponents play on these tricks.|sk||
